sect1.para:
The file is split into sections, defined as follows : [section-type] "[section-name]"
{
    // Section description
}
 Example: light "Light0"
{
    type directional
    colour 1.0 1.0 1.0
    intensity 0.8 1.0
}
 Some sections can have child subsections : material "Bronze"
{
    pass
    {
        ambient 0.2125 0.1275 0.054
        diffuse 0.714 0.4284 0.12144
        emissive 0.0
        specular 0.393548 0.271906 0.166721
        shininess 25.6
    }
}
